This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper discusses the issue of censoring due to interventions, which suggests that it may also belong to the computational epidemiology (cs.CE) sub-category.
